creator: Efficient Foundations
descriptionHtml:
Queensland Urban Utilities are responsible for delivering drinking water, recycled water and sewerage services to over 1.4 million customers across South East Queensland.

This app is designed to allow our employees to launch, complete and submit corporate eForms from any location within our service territory using a web-enabled device.

As such, this app is only available for use by Queensland Urban Utilities employees.
descriptionShort: This app is designed to allow our employees to launch complete and submit eForms
title: QUU eForms
